snippet.title: Haunt Trailer (0.9 Beta)
snippet.description:
Haunt (originally named The Real Slender Game what was a terrible idea :)) is indie horror game project inspired by Parsec Production "Slender: The Eight Pages" and Victors Surge Slender-man idea. If you like our game, please, support us in any way you can:

Official website: http://haunt-slendergame.com/

IndieDB: http://www.indiedb.com/games/haunt-the-real-slender-game
Steam: http://steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles/filedetails/?id=108401386
Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/pages/Haunt-The-Real-Slender-Game/383858555029358
